node.text:
Using Lightroom mobile app to edit up 8 photos from Amalfi last summer, I edited using my presets from @doyoutravelpresets that are included in The Preset Bundle.
I used to take sooo long to edit each image & now I can edit soo quickly, a fun way I explained presets to a friend was that they are a creators years of experience & practice packaged into a 1 step editing process ☺️
Link to the Preset Bundle https://www.thepresetbundle.com/?ref=gypsealust

node.title: Editing 8 pictures in 10 minutes- Tips & Tricks!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by lauren bullen on August 01, 2021 tagging @aperolspritzofficial. May be an image of pool.

node.text:
Spent the last 3 days in the Aperol Summer House, & ended our time with a sunset cruise around Paros, sipping of course #AperolSpritz 🧡🍊, dancing until the sun went down & swimming in the Aegean sea! 

Also guys, I’ve loved seeing all of you sharing with me your Aperol moments from around the world, feels like we’re celebrating together 😍 tag @gypsea_lust and @aperolspritzofficial and use the hashtags #AperolSpritz & #AperolSummerHouse so I can see them all!

Thank you @AperolSpritzOfficial for such a fun time with new friends!!

#AperolSpritzInParos #TogetherWeJoy

node.text: There’s something about Greece in the summer, I can’t get enough 🇬🇷🇬🇷

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by lauren bullen on July 30, 2021 tagging @aperolspritzofficial. May be an image of 1 person, standing, drink and outdoors.

node.text:
Been sipping Aperol Spritz all summer long & then the dream became a reality and I ended up back in Greece to celebrate the Aperol event yesterday here in Paros 🇬🇷 Even more perfect to be served an @aperolspritzofficial from this car/boat/bar/DJ 🤭 shared with old & new friends 🥰🍊🙌🏼🧡

#AperolSpritz #AperolSummerHouse #AperolSpritzInParos #TogetherWeJoy
